reference "eq:beta_A"

\end_inset

.
 Then, the left hand side of 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand formatted
reference "eq:beta_A"

\end_inset

 is non-decreasing in 
\begin_inset Formula $\beta_{A}$
\end_inset

, growing from zero to some value greater than 
\begin_inset Formula $\beta$
\end_inset

.
